{"id":140199,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：日震灾确认4314人死亡/","date":"2011-03-16T20:30:11Z","modified":"2011-03-16T20:38:05Z","title":"简讯：日震灾确认4314人死亡","content":"<div>\n<p>日本警察厅周三（16日）午夜公布说，东日本地震灾害迄今造成4314人死亡、8606人失踪。</p>\n<p>警察厅公布的统计表显示，重灾区宫城县是死亡人数最多的地区，达2244人。</p>\n<p>确认1482人死亡的岩手县则还有3318人失踪。</p>\n<p>发生核电站事故的福岛县设立了446个避难所，安置了13万多避难的灾民。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dETN4TU9kHaE4vGGk7ZwVWfuUaY/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dETN4TU9kHaE4vGGk7ZwVWfuUaY/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dETN4TU9kHaE4vGGk7ZwVWfuUaY/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dETN4TU9kHaE4vGGk7ZwVWfuUaY/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:clraHZBW0_I\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=sNi6brDGLxs:kO_Ej_MAjuU:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/sNi6brDGLxs\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):fanqiangyakexi